<section class="py-20 bg-[#f8f5f0]" data-controller="apply-modal">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    
    <a href="/membership">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm uppercase">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Membership
      </span>
    </a>

    <div class="text-center mb-16 mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-[0.1em] font-light mb-4 font-austin text-gray-900">
        FOUNDING MEMBERSHIP
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Own a piece of ROOM 13 · Limited to 130 members
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
      <div class="w-full mb-6 md:float-right md:ml-8 md:mb-4 md:max-w-sm">
        <%= image_tag "landing/16.jpeg", alt: "Room 13 event", class: "w-full h-auto border-5 border-white shadow-xl" %>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg tracking-[0.1em] font-montserrat mb-6">
        Founding Membership represents the highest tier of belonging within ROOM 13—not merely as a member, but as an owner. This is an invitation to shape the very fabric of our community, to have a voice in its direction, and to leave an indelible mark on its legacy.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg tracking-[0.1em] font-montserrat mb-6">
        Limited to just 130 visionaries worldwide, Founding Membership is designed for those who understand that the most meaningful experiences in the art world come from genuine investment—of time, passion, and purpose. As a Founding Member, you don't just participate in ROOM 13's story; you help write it.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg tracking-[0.1em] font-montserrat mb-6 font-bold">
        "We wanted to create something rare—a community where every member has skin in the game, where ownership breeds responsibility, and where shared investment creates bonds that transcend typical social connections."
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg tracking-[0.1em] font-montserrat mb-6">
        You'll be invited to our exclusive annual retreat - an intimate gathering where Founding Members convene to reflect, connect, and shape the year ahead. And with the flexibility to pause your membership for up to three years, your stake in ROOM 13 remains secure through life's many chapters.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg tracking-[0.1em] font-montserrat mb-6">
        Beyond ownership, Founding Members enjoy preferred VIP access to our extensive network of over 50 partner fairs and cultural institutions. We will utilise our network to ensure you are always among the first to experience the art world's most anticipated moments.
      </p>

      <div class="clear-both"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Benefits Section -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 shadow-sm mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-austin tracking-[0.1em] text-gray-900 mb-6 border-b border-gray-200 pb-3">
        FOUNDING MEMBER BENEFITS
      </h3>
      
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">Guaranteed Access to All ROOM 13 Events</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">Including a +1 guest at every event</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">Preferred Partner Access</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">Priority access to 50+ partner fairs & events globally</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">A Global Community</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">Connect with like-minded art enthusiasts, collectors, and cultural leaders worldwide</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">Annual Member Retreat</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">An exclusive invitation to our intimate yearly gathering of Founding Members</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">Ownership & Voting Rights</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">A stake in ROOM 13 with a voice in shaping its future</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-900 mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-900 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em] font-medium block">Flexible Membership</span>
            <span class="text-gray-500 font-montserrat text-xs tracking-[0.05em]">Pause your membership for up to 3 years while retaining your ownership</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Limited Availability Notice -->
    <div class="bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 p-6 mb-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-700 font-montserrat text-sm tracking-[0.1em]">
        <strong>Limited Availability:</strong> Only 130 Founding Memberships will ever be offered.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Apply Section -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <button type="button" 
              data-action="click->apply-modal#open" 
              data-apply-modal-type-param="founding"
              class="inline-block px-16 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-white tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-montserrat text-sm hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer">
        Apply Now
      </button>
      
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm tracking-[0.15em] font-montserrat mt-8">
        For enquiries, please <a href="mailto:irene@room13.art" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors duration-300 underline">talk to Irene</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <%= render 'memberships/apply_modal', default_membership: 'founding' %>
</section>
